#: src/uagent/cli_startup.py:22
msgid ""
"Select tool genres to enable at startup.\n"
"1: comm  - Communication (Teams, Discord, etc.)\n"
"2: office - Office suite (Excel, Word, etc.)\n"
"4: devel  - Development (lint, py_compile, test, etc.)\n"
"Enter the sum of values (e.g., 3 = comm + office, 7 = all, or press Enter to enable all):"
msgstr ""
"स्टार्टअपवर सक्षम करण्यासाठी टूल प्रकार निवडा।\n"
"1: comm  - संवाद (Teams, Discord, इ.)\n"
"2: office - ऑफिस सूट (Excel, Word, इ.)\n"
"4: devel  - विकास (lint, py_compile, test, इ.)\n"
"मूल्यांची बेरीज प्रविष्ट करा (उदा. 3 = comm + office, 7 = सर्व, किंवा सर्व सक्षम करण्यासाठी Enter दाबा):"

